Polar Capital Hldgs (POLR)



Polar Capital Hldgs

Appointment of Chief Executive

RNS Number : 1750L Polar Capital Holdings PLC 17 July 2017  

17 July 2017                                               
Polar Capital Holdings plc
Appointment of Chief Executive - Gavin Rochussen
Further to the announcements made on 19 January 2017 (RNS 5468U and RNS 5473U) Polar Capital Holdings plc ("Polar Capital" or the "Group"), today announces the appointment of Gavin Rochussen as an Executive Director and he has taken up his duties as Chief Executive.  Gavin has also become a partner of Polar Capital LLP.
Mr Tim Woolley has with effect from today relinquished his executive duties and has moved to a non-executive position.
Tom Bartlam, Chairman of Polar Capital, commented: "I am delighted that Gavin Rochussen has taken up his post as our new Chief Executive. Gavin has an exceptional record as a CEO in the asset management industry and has a proven record in developing an institutional and overseas business, both areas of potential growth for Polar Capital in future years."
Share Award and Shareholdings
As announced on 19 January 2017 (RNS 5473U), on taking up his role as Chief Executive, Mr Rochussen has joined the Group's Executive Incentive Plan and has been granted a deferred, forfeitable award to the value of three million pounds (the "Award") of ordinary shares of the Group ("Ordinary Shares"). In order to satisfy the Award the Group's Employee Benefit Trust purchased 802,967 Ordinary Shares at an average purchase price of 373.6P per share. The Award vests in three equal traches on the first, second and third anniversary of its granting. This comprises the total interest of Mr Rochussen in Ordinary Shares under the Executive Incentive Plan.
Also as announced on 19 January, Mr Rochussen purchased a beneficial interest in one million Ordinary Shares which are held in the name of Amigona Holdings Inc. 
Enquiries:




Polar Capital Holdings PLC
Gavin Rochussen (CEO)
John Mansell (COO)


+44 (0)20 7227 2700




Canaccord Genuity - Nomad and Joint Broker
