Polar Capital Global Healthcare Growth and Income Trust Share Offer: share allocation
Polar Capital Global Healthcare Growth and Income Trust shares have now been allocated to investors.
Allocation of shares
Shares have been allocated in full.
How to deal Polar Capital Global Healthcare Growth and Income Trust shares:
If you missed out on the share offer then dealing beings at 08:00 on 20 June on the London Stock Exchange.
For further information, please take a look at our Polar Capital Global Healthcare Growth and Income Trust frequently asked questions. Alternatively, please email [email protected] or call us on 01296 41 46 75.













